1649
01:49:38,733 --> 01:49:43,101
You use the syringes in the kit to switch
the liquids in the two medication vials.

1650
01:49:43,101 --> 01:49:46,072
And, as a final precaution,

1651
01:49:47,994 --> 01:49:53,222
