the life saving antidote.

1652
01:49:53,621 --> 01:49:55,847
No, no. That's impossible.

1653
01:49:56,073 --> 01:49:57,516
It is the truth.

1654
01:49:57,687 --> 01:50:00,242
Hand me that vial of morphine,
I'll show you.

1655
01:50:00,242 --> 01:50:05,229
